1
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,720
Who?

2
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,680
Fan, listen to me.

3
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:25,840
Fan!

4
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,440
Fan!

5
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,640
Fan!

6
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,850
Stop! Stop running!

7
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,320
Fan! Fan!

8
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,520
We can talk this over.

9
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,320
You found a gold mine.

10
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,560
Yes, exactly.

11
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,360
Look, Fan.

12
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,180
Everyone gets a share.

13
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,650
We'll cut you in.

14
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,040
Just don't tell anyone.

15
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,880
No.

16
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,840
I'm going back to tell Fei.

17
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,640
But then you won't get any money.

18
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,160
Right?

19
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:19,600
Me, Qiang, Yong.

20
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:21,840
Four shares.

21
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,360
One for each of us.

22
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,720
You could get a lot of money, you know?

23
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,370
I don't believe you.

24
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,640
Come on, when have I ever lied to you?

25
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,280
Right?

26
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,680
Just calm down first.

27
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,760
Listen to me.

28
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,140
I'm going back to tell Fei.

29
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,880
Zhang, make sure you're recording this.

30
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:15,760
I'll take notes.

31
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:16,560
Officer.

32
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:20,680
We're all security guards for Shanshui Group.

33
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,720
We patrol the mountains.

34
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,560
Luo Zhengqiang and I were on patrol at the time.

35
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:29,240
Yang Gaoyong had just finished visiting his parents' graves,

36
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,680
and was coming to meet us.

37
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,440
Then, right at that moment,

38
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,800
we heard a scream.

39
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,860
So we rushed over there immediately.

40
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:39,480
But Fan had already fallen off the cliff.

41
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:44,079
After that, Qiang arrived too.

42
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:49,240
I heard the noise and brought my men over.

43
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,760
Yang Gang, Yang Gaoyong, and Luo Zhengqiang.

44
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:54,320
They are indeed part of our security team.

45
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:56,480
They are responsible for patrolling the mountains.

46
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,079
Illegal mining has been rampant lately,

47
00:03:58,079 --> 00:04:00,680
so Shanshui Group ordered strict patrols

48
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,120
to protect the mines.

49
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,020
Your statements check out so far.

50
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,880
Regarding Fan's fall,

51
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,540
we will investigate further.

52
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:11,240
We may need your cooperation later on.

53
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,480
No problem.

54
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,880
Of course. And because it's Fan...

55
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,360
we all knew him.

56
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:20,440
We watched him grow up.

57
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,760
If you have any questions about him,

58
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,620
however you need us to cooperate,

59
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,000
just come to us anytime.

60
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,200
Alright then. You can go back for now.

61
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,720
Yang Gang.

62
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,800
When Fan died,

63
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,740
the three of you were at the scene.

64
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,840
What exactly happened?

65
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,320
Sit.

66
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:20,800
We were just patrolling the mountain at the time.

67
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,120
We heard a scream.

68
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,980
We ran over to check immediately.

69
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,490
By the time we got there,

70
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:30,920
Fan had already fallen to his death.

71
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:41,280
This Zhanlu Sword is a local specialty.

72
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,290
It was an heirloom in Fan's family.

73
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,800
He gave it to me for my birthday.

74
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:53,300
I really treated him like a younger brother.

75
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,400
So, Yang Gang,

76
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,120
I want you to tell me the truth.

77
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:11,010
Liao Fei, I know you value loyalty.

78
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,560
I watched Fan grow up too.

79
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,690
What happened to him...

80
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:20,200
it truly breaks my heart.

81
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,800
I regret this too.

82
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,040
Okay.

83
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,360
I understand.

84
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:40,120
I hope you had nothing to do with this.

85
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:55,920
Gangzi, starting today,

86
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,840
the three of you don't need to come to work anymore.

87
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,040
Why?

88
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,120
Is it because of what happened to Xiaofan?

89
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,920
About Xiaofan... I really don't know the details.

90
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,250
Did Situ say something?

91
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:13,720
You should ask the higher-ups for details.

92
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:14,640
Fine.

93
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,360
What right do you have to fire us?

94
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:23,160
This is your contract termination agreement.

95
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:23,960
Sign it.

96
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,840
What do you mean?

97
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,440
What do I mean?

98
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:32,640
Ever since you joined the security team,

99
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:35,640
Xiaofan fell off a cliff and got hurt in the mine blast.

100
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,760
Does that really have nothing to do with you?

101
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,720
We were on patrol when Xiaofan fell.

102
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,040
We didn't force him to jump.

103
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,280
What about the injury from the blast?

104
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:44,840
He knew about the blasting, but he still ran into the mine.

105
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:47,370
The site needs to be cleared before blasting.

106
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:50,440
Yongzi went in to check if anyone was still inside.

107
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,840
We did our job.

108
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:52,800
And now you're blaming us?

109
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,600
Don't give me that nonsense.

110
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,840
You are using your position as security guards to steal ore.

111
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,120
It's an inside job.

112
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:03,000
Steal ore? Is there gold or diamonds in your mine?

113
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,360
What kind of ore is worth... Yongzi!

114
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,120
Miss Situ.

115
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,920
This whole incident,

116
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,420
was my decision alone.

117
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,800
I told them to go on patrol.

118
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,200
I also told them to enter the mine.

119
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,680
If you're going to fire someone,

120
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,720
I beg you,

121
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,640
just fire me alone, okay?

122
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,600
Brother, you can't fire Gangzi.

123
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:30,600
We've all seen how hard Gangzi works.

124
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,320
Uncle Tian.

125
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,679
This is all because of me. No need to drag everyone else into it.

126
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,610
Stay out of this.

127
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,320
Do you know how many thieves

128
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:39,440
have their eyes on those abandoned mines?

129
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:42,919
What is wrong with Gangzi taking people to check on them?

130
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,400
If it weren't for people like Gangzi,

131
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:48,200
the ore in our mine would have been stolen long ago.

132
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,400
Miss Situ.

133
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,280
If you fire Gangzi today,

134
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,960
then fire me, Old Tian, too.

135
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,800
Fire all of us!

136
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:59,800
You can't fire him! You can't!

137
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,520
What are you doing? Are you trying to rebel?

138
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:03,320
This is the company's decision.

139
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,410
About what happened today,

140
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,250
I will investigate it thoroughly.

141
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:26,840
Mr. Xiao.

142
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,370
You were looking for me?

143
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,200
Have a seat.

144
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,920
Mr. Xiao.

145
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,280
What's going on?

146
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,010
Is something wrong?

147
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:52,760
No, just tell me what it is.

148
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:58,890
There is something.

149
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:04,840
I'm afraid you might do something rash after I tell you.

150
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,400
Mr. Xiao.

151
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:11,680
We can just speak plainly.

152
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,280
We are brothers.

153
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,600
You're right, Fei.

154
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,440
We are brothers.

155
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:21,720
Brothers should be honest with each other, right?

156
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,760
Right.

157
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:24,720
Xiaoqiang.

158
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,800
Brother Fei. Mr. Xiao.

159
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,520
Come, sit.

160
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,320
This is...

161
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:39,440
Ah Qiang.

162
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:43,920
Tell Fei exactly what you heard and saw.

163
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:44,780
Tell the truth.

164
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,000
Okay, Mr. Xiao.

165
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,080
Fei.

166
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,200
I heard the sound of a chase.

167
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,960
So I rushed over.

168
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,920
I saw Yang Gang,

169
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:57,600
Yang Gaoyong, and Luo Zhengqiang surrounding Fan.

170
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,560
I hid in the bushes.

171
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,000
What the four of them were saying,

172
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,200
I couldn't hear clearly.

173
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,920
It was too far. Then, after a while,

174
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:08,240
Fan suddenly turned and ran.

175
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,080
And they chased after him.

176
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,440
And then...

177
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:13,600
Then what?

178
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,960
What are you afraid of?

179
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,280
Just say what you saw.

180
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:22,120
Then Yang Gang pushed Fan off the cliff.

181
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,600
Is that true?

182
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:28,540
I'm asking you!

183
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:30,840
Let go.

184
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,560
Fei, this has nothing to do with me.

185
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,200
I'm not lying.

186
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,440
I'm telling the truth.

187
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:44,400
I saw Yang Gang push Fan off the cliff with my own eyes.

188
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,640
I was totally stunned.

189
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,640
Fei, where are you going?

190
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,640
Where am I going?

191
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,600
I'm going to find Yang Gang.

192
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,440
Come back.

193
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:55,360
What?

194
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,080
Fei.

195
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,540
You're my brother, you know that?

196
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,120
Do you know why I didn't tell you earlier?

197
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,560
I was afraid you'd do something rash.

198
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:11,280
Mr. Xiao, stay out of this.

199
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,280
I know how to handle my own business.
